ir manner of speaking is looked down upon and results in them not being taken seriously, as if their accent discredits the validity of what they are saying.%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a%3c https://www.nbcnews.com/news/latino/latina-council-member-nancy-navarro-accent-mocked-claps-back-pride-rcna354%0a%3c %0a%3c [[#contentends]]%0a%3c ----%0a\ No newline at end of file%0a
